ẫn còn nghi ngờ. Đêm diễn ra sự kiện dẫn đến đám tang đó, Vee đã bị thương và có những điều anh không thể nhớ. Anh sẽ biết rằng anh không phải là người duy nhất tuyệt vọng muốn biết những gì thực sự đã xảy ra đêm đó.</p>","tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"153915","season":1,"vote_average":7,"vote_count":3},"modified":"2025-10-02T10:40:29.000Z","cast":["Chanon Santinatornkul","Worranit Thawornwong","Voravudh Niyomsap","Patara Eksangkul","Chatchawit Techarukpong","Harit Cheewagaroon","Dusita Kitisarakulchai","Most Witsarut","Poramaporn Jangkamol","Khunakorn Kirdpan"],"director":["Petch Warayu Rakkul","พีรพล เธียรเจริญ"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chanon Santinatornkul","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chanon Santinatornkul","tmdb_id":1353678,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/osG0qvkXtpO0DPiZKlSllAVjTlE.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1353678"},{"name":"Worranit Thawornwong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Worranit Thawornwong","tmdb_id":1889502,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/xqV4ana4pzUkIjloiVPR9yjkJNH.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1889502"},{"name":"Voravudh Niyomsap","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Voravudh Niyomsap","tmdb_id":1345539,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5F4ltTHkGxNpzNUtk6wTAHHxP8G.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1345539"},{"name":"Patara Eksangkul","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Patara Eksangkul","tmdb_id":2860552,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6JHIVa9EWVt6bBbOEnxngxZ74tf.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2860552"},{"name":"Chatchawit Techarukpong","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chatchawit Techarukpong","tmdb_id":2214738,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/8TzHVNq9FPGsY5ArtccLFEYhL0r.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2214738"},{"name":"Harit Cheewagaroon","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Harit Cheewagaroon","tmdb_id":1833840,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lMLLtZcFueZ6icN8FAnD7Go9DmQ.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.t